---
layout: base
title: Home
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Jerusalem Tech Blog</h1>
    <p>Exploring the intersection of ancient wisdom and cutting-edge technology in the heart of Jerusalem</p>
    <a href="/posts/" class="btn">Read Our Blog</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="featured-posts">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Latest Articles</h2>
    
    <div class="posts-grid">
      {% assign posts = collections.posts | reverse %}
      {% for post in posts limit:6 %}
        <article class="post-card">
          {% if post.data.image %}
            <div class="post-card-image" style="background-image: url('{{ post.data.image }}')"></div>
          {% else %}
            <div class="post-card-image" style="background-image: url('/assets/images/default-post.jpg')"></div>
          {% endif %}
          
          <div class="post-card-content">
            <div class="post-card-date">{{ post.date | dateFormat }}</div>
            <h3 class="post-card-title">
              <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
            </h3>
            <div class="post-card-excerpt">
              {% if post.data.excerpt %}
                {{ post.data.excerpt }}
              {% else %}
                {{ post.templateContent | strip_html | truncate: 150 }}
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card-link">Read More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/posts/" class="btn">View All Posts</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-preview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-section">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/assets/images/jerusalem-tech-hub.jpg" alt="Jerusalem Tech Hub" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <h2>Where Ancient Meets Innovation</h2>
        <p>Jerusalem, a city with over 3,000 years of history, is rapidly emerging as a vibrant tech hub. Our blog explores this unique intersection where ancient wisdom meets cutting-edge innovation.</p>
        <p>From startup success stories to deep dives into the latest technologies, we cover the dynamic tech ecosystem flourishing in this historic city.</p>
        <a href="/about/" class="btn">Learn More About Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="topics-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Popular Topics</h2>
    
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="topic-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Startups</h3>
        <p>Discover the innovative startups emerging from Jerusalem's tech ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="topic-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="topic-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>AI & Machine Learning</h3>
        <p>Explore cutting-edge AI research and applications being developed locally.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="topic-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="topic-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Web Development</h3>
        <p>Stay updated on the latest web technologies, frameworks, and best practices.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="topic-card animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="topic-icon">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Cybersecurity</h3>
        <p>Learn about advancements in cybersecurity from Israel's renowned security experts.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .text-center {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .featured-posts,
  .topics-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .featured-posts h2,
  .topics-section h2 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .featured-posts h2::after,
  .topics-section h2::after {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 80px;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
  }
  
  .topics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .topic-card {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
  }
  
  .topic-card.in-view {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
  
  .topic-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }
  
  .topic-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .topic-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .topic-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .about-preview {
    background-color: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .topics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    }
    
    .featured-posts,
    .topics-section,
    .about-preview {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }
  }
</style>
